0the%20two%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20one%20had%20a%20lower%20floor%20than%20the%20other%2C%20so%20the%20engineering%20side%20cost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20whole%20costings%20were%20around%20%24160%2C000%20(%24173%2C296).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFalling%20in%20love%20with%20Sicily%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22872%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drone%20footage%20of%20Sambuca%20di%20Sicilia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b28ad743bb77284ba092b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrone%20footage%20of%20Sambuca%20di%20Sicilia.%3Cp%3ELuke%20Renard%3B%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGary%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20think%20one%20of%20the%20things%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20during%20all%20this%20was%20the%20people%20of%20Sambuca.%20Everyone%20has%20been%20super%20welcoming%20and%20friendly%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20small%20town%20that%20feels%20very%20international.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETam%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20are%20also%20people%20who%20have%20lived%20here%20for%20generations%20and%20generations%2C%20who%20are%20so%20nice%2C%20cool%2C%20and%20ready%20to%20make%20friends%20with%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGary%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEveryone%20we%20have%20talked%20to%20in%20this%20town%20has%20had%20a%20great%20experience%2C%20so%20I%20think%20it%20tells%20you%20something%20about%20the%20people.%20They%20see%20the%20value%20in%20outsiders%20boosting%20the%20economy%20and%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20the%20one-euro%20program%20was%20brilliant%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20because%20it%20gave%20some%20people%20a%20chance%20to%20get%20houses%20for%20very%20little%20money%2C%20and%20it%20brought%20us%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20get%20to%20live%20this%20sort%20of%20dream%3B%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2