%20would%20enable%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20punish%20violations%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2076-year-old%20war%20veteran%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20pursuit%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%20has%20exposed%20the%20opacity%20surrounding%20political%20funding.%20His%20scrutiny%20work%20on%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20despite%20facing%20threats%20and%20intimidation%2C%20led%20to%20over%2080%20RTI%20requests%20and%20a%20major%20expose%20in%202019%2C%20revealing%20the%20scheme%E2%80%99s%20flaws%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20accountability%20in%20political%20funding%2C%20which%20finally%20resulted%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20banning%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20declared%20in%202019%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20had%20iterated%20its%202013%20advisory%20against%20the%20use%20of%20photos%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdefence%20personnel%20by%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Celection%20propaganda%E2%80%9D%20after%20former%20naval%20chief%20Admiral%20L.%20Ramdas%20complained%20about%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20posters%20that%20featured%20an%20image%20of%20Wing%20Commander%20V.%20Abhinandan%2C%20who%20was%20released%20by%20Pakistan%20after%20his%20fighter%20jet%20was%20shot%20down%20over%20its%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20commission%20that%20some%20political%20parties%20are%20using%20the%20photographs%20of%20the%20Defence%20personnel%20in%20advertisement%20as%20part%20of%20their%20political%20campaigns%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20noted%20in%20its%20March%209%2C%202019%20advisory.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20a%20nation%20are%20the%20guardian%20of%20its%20frontiers%2C%20security%20and%20the%20political%20system.%20They%20are%20apolitical%20and%20neutral%20stakeholders%20in%20a%20modern%20democracy.%20It%20is%20therefore%20necessary%20that%20the%20political%20parties%20and%20leaders%20exercise%20great%20caution%20while%20making%20any%20reference%20to%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20in%20their%20political%20campaigns%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ECI%20added.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20March%2019%2C%202019%20the%20ECI%20had%20issued%20another%20advisory%20extending%20to%20social%20media%20against%20any%20electioneering%20about%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20underlined%20the%20repeated%20instances%20of%20violation%20of%20the%20advisory%20by%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%20for%20using%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9CModi%20%3Ci%3Eji%20ki%20sena%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Ghaziabad%20on%20March%2031%2C%202019%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20cross-border%20strikes%20by%20Indian%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%209%2C%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20in%20Latur%3A%20%E2%80%9CMy%20first-time%20voters%2C%20can%20you%20dedicate%20your%20first%20vote%20to%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20air%20strike%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Balakot%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20on%20April%2025%2C%202019%20the%20prime%20minister%20repeated%20the%20Balakot%20pitch%20in%20Varanasi.%20On%20April%2021%2C%20Modi%20said%20in%20Barmer%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20we%20kept%20it%20(the%20nuclear%20button)%20for%20Diwali%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20same%20day%2C%20he%20said%20in%20Patan%3A%20%E2%80%9CPakistan%20announced%20the%20return%20of%20the%20pilot%E2%80%A6%20else%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20%3Ci%3Eqatal%20ki%20raat%3C%2Fi%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20Batra%20had%20also%20complained%20against%20a%20BJP%20hoarding%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20image%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%E2%80%9CEntered%20the%20home%20of%20the%20enemy%20and%20attacked%20the%20terrorists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commission-has-no-comments-on-landmark-verdict-on-electoral-bonds-how-it-changed-its-stance%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20Has%20No%20Comments%20on%20Landmark%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Verdict%3A%20How%20it%20Changed%20its%20Stance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20ECI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20any%20of%20these%20violative%20of%20the%20election%20code.%20However%2C%20former%20election%20commissioner%20Ashok%20Lavasa%20had%20registered%20dissent%20notes%20to%20these%20clean%20chits.%20He%20joined%20the%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20after%20leaving%20the%20ECI%20later%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2019-model-code-modi-violation%5C%22%3EECI%20was%20criticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20acting%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20violation%20of%20the%20model%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20poll%20panel%2C%20Congress%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-may-approach-courts-against-modi-shahs-repeated-violations-of-mcc%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%20in%20April%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20labelled%20the%20ECI%20as%20%E2%80%9CElection%20Omission%E2%80%9D%20and%20wondered%20whether%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20were%20outside%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20MCC%2C%20which%20he%20dubbed%20as%20%E2%80%9CModi%20code%20of%20conduct%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20(open)%20letter%20(to%20the%20CEC)%20is%20to%20prevent%20such%20situations%20once%20the%20MCC%20is%20in%20place%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20Batra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709632740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09195651%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fstrengthen-model-code-to-curb-politicisation-of-armed-forces-lokesh-batra-to-eci%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Batra%20referred%20to%20the%20advisory%20issued%20by%20the%20ECI%20on%20March%209%2C%202019%20asking%20'political%20parties%2Fcandidates%20to%20desist%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20election%20campaigning%2C%20from%20indulging%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20political%20propaganda%20involving%20activities%20of%20the%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fstrengthen-model-code-to-curb-politicisation-of-armed-forces-lokesh-batra-to-eci%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turkey%20detains%20seven%20suspected%20of%20selling%20information%20to%20Israel's%20Mossad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709632691000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108235182%2Cimgsize-800320.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad%2Farticleshow%2F108235092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108235092.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETurkish%20police%20detain%207%2C%20including%20private%20detective%2C%20suspected%20of%20selling%20info%20to%20Mossad.%20Detective%20trained%20in%20Belgrade%2C%20received%20cryptocurrency%20payments.%20Turkish-Israeli%20tensions%20rise%20amidst%20Hamas%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad%2Farticleshow%2F108235092.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad%2Famp_articleshow%2F108235092.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fturkey-detains-seven-suspected-of-selling-information-to-israels-mossad%2Famp_articleshow%2F108235092.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Dismisses%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%20Against%20DK%20Shivakumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20relief%20to%20Karnataka's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20dismissed%20a%202018%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader.%20The%20case%20pertained%20to%20allegations%20of%20tax%20evasion%20and%20hawala%20transactions%20worth%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20was%20arrested%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20officials%20in%20September%202019%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case.%20The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20granted%20him%20bail%20the%20next%20month.%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20had%20then%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20political%20vendetta%20and%20said%20he%20had%20full%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20investigation%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader%20had%20followed%20Income%20Tax%20department's%20raids%20on%20premises%20linked%20to%20him%20and%20his%20aides%20in%202017.%20Officials%20had%20then%20said%20cash%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%20300%20crore%20was%20recovered%20in%20these%20raids.%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20had%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20cash%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuestion%20of%20whether%20120B%20IPC%20can%20constitute%20a%20predicate%20standalone%20offence%20to%20enable%20ED%20to%20invoke%20PMLA%20has%20already%20been%20decided%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20that%20criminal%20conspiracy%20-%20under%20120%20B%20of%20IPC%20-%20will%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20only%20if%20the%20alleged%20conspiracy%20is%20to%20commit%20an%20offence%20included%20in%20the%20Schedule%20to%20the%20Act.%20The%20ED%20has%20sought%20a%20review%20of%20this%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20today%20said%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20free%20to%20see%20a%20recall%20of%20today's%20order%20if%20the%20review%20request%20is%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%20had%20in%202019%20approached%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20and%20sought%20dismissal%20of%20summons%20issued%20by%20ED.%20On%20finding%20no%20relief%20there%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20corruption%20case%20against%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20political%20row%20in%20Karnataka%20at%20this%20point.%20The%20Siddaramaiah-led%20government%20recently%20withdrew%20the%20sanction%20to%20CBI%20to%20probe%20the%20case.%20The%20central%20agency%2C%20which%20got%20a%20go-ahead%20in%20the%20case%20before%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20now%20challenged%20the%20new%20government's%20move%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shivakumar%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20harassing%20him%20by%20misusing%20central%20agencies.%20Responding%20to%20today's%20order%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%20told%20NDTV%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20relief%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20troubled.%20Today%20is%20a%20great%20day%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709632680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fgtddtb7g_dk-shivakumar-pti-650_650x400_16_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-chief-minister-dk-shivakumar-5179730%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20dismisses%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-chief-minister-dk-shivakumar-5179730%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-chief-minister-dk-shivakumar-5179730%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-chief-minister-dk-shivakumar-5179730%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20and%20Rihanna's%20picture%20goes%20VIRAL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709632162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108234800%2Cimgsize-36054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-rihannas-picture-from-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-pre-wedding-bash-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F108234800.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108234800.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20his%20family%2C%20wife%20Gauri%20Khan%20and%20children%20Aryan%20Khan%2C%20Suhana%20Khan%2C%20and%20AbRam%2C%20had%20a%20gala%20time%20at%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20son%20Anant%20Ambani%20and%20Radhika%20Merchant's%20pre-wedding%20festivities%20in%20Jamnagar%2C%20Gujarat.%20This%20star-studded%20event%20featured%20performances%20by%20numerous%20Indian%20and%20international%20artists%2C%20including%20pop%20diva%20Rihanna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-rihannas-picture-from-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-pre-wedding-bash-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F108234800.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20Absence%20of%20All%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20Manipur%20Passes%20Bill%20Criminalising%20Changing%20Names%20of%20Places%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F05160550%2FDhL0M9tUYAEIhu0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Manipur%20assembly%20has%20passed%20a%20Bill%20that%20has%20made%20changing%20existing%20names%20of%20places%20in%20the%20strife-torn%20north-eastern%20state%20a%20punishable%20offence%20with%20an%20imprisonment%20up%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passage%20of%20this%20Bill%20at%20the%20ongoing%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20all%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20second%20official%20move%20by%20the%20legislators%2C%20across%20party%20lines%20belonging%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20aimed%20at%20preserving%20its%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20Winter%20Session%20on%20February%2028%2C%20all%20Meitei%20MLAs%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20urge%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20end%20its%20ongoing%20suspension%20of%20operations%20with%20all%20the%20Kuki%20armed%20groups%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20violating%20ground%20rules%20and%20attacking%20Meiteis%20during%20the%20ethnic%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Names%20of%20Places%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20on%20March%204%2C%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20criminalised%20attempts%20made%20by%20any%20person%20to%20refer%20to%20some%20places%20with%20their%20own%20names%20in%20official%20statements%2C%20etc.%20From%20the%20instances%20given%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20at%20the%20House%2C%20it%20comes%20across%20that%20the%20law%20was%20particularly%20aimed%20at%20stalling%20the%20Kuki%20community%20to%20act%20otherwise.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20Churachandpur%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20Lamka%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20made%20a%20specific%20reference%20to%20this%20particular%20example%20in%20the%20House%20on%20March%204%2C%20stating%20that%20Churachandpur%20was%20named%20after%20Maharaja%20Churachand%20(of%20Manipur%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community)%20in%20honour%20of%20his%20contributions%20made%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20territorial%20boundary%20of%20Manipur.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20no%20one%20is%20authorised%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20a%20place%20or%20site%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20authority%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fhouse-passes-manipur-names-of-places-bill-2024%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20Imphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20mentioned%20use%20of%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Lamka%20district%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20Churachandpur%20district%20in%20an%20official%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ongoing%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20several%20instances%20came%20to%20light%20where%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20change%20names%20on%20community%20lines%2C%20including%20a%20case%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fin-suspected-hacking-imphal-airport-ticketing-office-called-lamka-on-e-tickets%5C%22%3Esuspected%20hacking%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Air%20India%E2%80%99s%20ticketing%20office%20(ATO)%20at%20Imphal%20in%20July%20last%20year.%20Tickets%20issued%20to%20passengers%20at%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20were%20printed%20as%20ATO%2C%20Lamka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20complaints%20made%20by%20the%20Meitei%20passengers%2C%20MLA%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20R.%20Imo%20Singh%2C%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20civil%20aviation%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20to%20rectify%20the%20mistake%20and%20initiate%20an%20investigation%20into%20it%20immediately.%20Note%20that%20as%20of%20now%2C%20Kukis%20cannot%20access%20the%20Imphal%20airport%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20facility%20in%20the%20state%20providing%20connectivity%20outside%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20historical%20hill%20%E2%80%98Thangjing%E2%80%99%20was%20found%20trying%20to%20change%20into%20%E2%80%98Thangting%E2%80%99%20and%20Thangjing%20hill%20as%20Mount%20Olive%20and%20a%20reserved%20forest%20as%20%E2%80%98Haokip%20Reserve%20Forest%E2%80%99.%20Even%20some%20groups%20produced%20documents%20regarding%20the%20%E2%80%98Haokip%20Reserve%20Forest%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20unexpected%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20House%20on%20March%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20any%20attempt%20by%20an%20officer%20found%20involved%20in%20the%20alteration%20of%20any%20name%20from%20the%20official%20ones%20would%20be%20prosecuted%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20be%20imprisoned%20up%20to%20three%20years%20and%20Rs%201-3%20l