.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F21174235%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-21-at-5.42.18-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2028%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20announced%20the%202024-25%20cricket%20contracts%20for%20players.%20Much%20of%20it%20was%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98no-brainer%E2%80%99%20space.%20But%20there%20were%20some%20big%20questions%20as%20well.%20The%20answers%20to%20these%20questions%20have%20either%20not%20been%20given%2C%20or%20are%20hazy%20and%20contradictory.%20So%2C%20why%20this%20continued%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20the%20running%20of%20our%20favourite%20sport%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20discuss%20the%20obvious%20first%20question%20%E2%80%93%20Ishan%20Kishan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20Kishan%20hammered%20the%20fastest%20200%20on%20One%20Day%20cricket%20history%2C%20getting%20to%20the%20mark%20in%20just%20126%20balls%2C%20shattering%20Chris%20Gayle%E2%80%99s%20record%20by%2012%20balls.%20The%2024-year-old%20may%20have%20hoped%20that%20this%20ferocious%20double%20century%20would%20keep%20him%20busy%20in%202023%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20ODI%20and%20T20%20formats.%20He%20may%20have%20expected%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Test%20side%20as%20well%2C%20since%20Rishabh%20Pant%20was%20injured%2C%20and%20K.S.%20Bharat%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20doing%20much%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be.%20Kishan%20spent%20all%20of%202023%2C%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20in%20all%20forms%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIshan%20Kishan%20%E2%80%93%20many%20questions%2C%20no%20answers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20he%20getting%20picked%3F%20Why%20was%20Bharat%20preferred%20to%20him%3F%20It%20could%20not%20have%20been%20about%C2%A0%20his%20batting.%20If%20it%20was%20his%20keeping%2C%20was%20Kishan%20told%20it%20was%20not%20upto%20the%20mark%3F%20While%20he%20was%20repeatedly%20not%20being%20picked%2C%20was%20he%20being%20counselled%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kishan%20finally%20exited%2C%20citing%20mental%20fatigue%2C%20half%20way%20through%20the%20South%20Africa%20tour%20in%20December%202023%2C%20and%20then%20he%20also%20skipped%20the%20Ranji%20trophy%20games%C2%A0for%20his%20home%20state%20Jharkhand%2C%20he%20was%20overnight%20dubbed%20a%20%E2%80%98bad%20boy%E2%80%99.%20Was%20his%20mental%20health%20assessed%20at%20any%20point%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Shah%2C%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20secretary%20and%20%E2%80%98de%20facto%20boss%E2%80%99%2C%20targeted%20Kishan%20(without%20naming%20him)%20in%20a%20public%20speech%20in%20Rajkot.%20A%20few%20days%20later%20he%20lost%20his%20contract.%20But%20was%20it%20all%20Kishan%E2%80%99s%20fault%3F%20Could%20it%20be%20that%20the%20shabby%20treatment%20right%20through%202023%2C%20being%20stuck%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20affected%20his%20mental%20health%20and%20triggered%20his%20%E2%80%98rebellion%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20BCCI%20own%20its%20responsibility%20and%20give%20us%2C%20cricket%20fans%2C%20some%20idea%20about%20what%20actually%20happened%2C%20and%20how%20and%20why%20a%20highly%20talented%2C%20always%20gung-ho%20cricketer%E2%80%99s%20career%20went%20down%20the%20flush%3F%20Has%20the%20BCCI%20killed%20a%20career%2C%20by%20mis-managing%20this%20talented%20youngster%20from%20Jharkhand%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20Jayesh%20Shah%2C%C2%A0this%20is%20cricket%2C%20not%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20we%20are%20asking%20is%20%E2%80%93%20is%20this%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20BCCI%2C%20an%20opaque%20dictatorial%20BCCI%3F%20Or%20a%20BCCI%20that%20reflects%20the%20values%20of%20cricket%20heroes%20like%20Roger%20Binny%2C%20the%20current%20BCCI%20president%2C%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20our%20current%20coach%2C%20or%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20the%20current%20chief%20selector%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20even%20the%20values%20of%20our%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20has%20also%20been%20Kishan%E2%80%99s%20captain%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20for%20years.%20The%20near%20total%20silence%20on%20Kishan%20from%20all%20these%20gentlemen%2C%20suggests%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98super%20power%E2%80%99%20leaning%20on%20them%20to%20say%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20silence%2C%20how%20about%C2%A0Kishan%E2%80%99s%20own%20version%20of%20events%3F%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20he%20be%20allowed%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%3F%20Clearly%20not.%20He%E2%80%99s%20been%20silent%20for%20months.%20Perhaps%20not%20keen%20to%20rile%20up%20BCCI%20any%20further.%20But%20should%20that%20be%20the%20nature%20of%20a%20player%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20his%20sport%E2%80%99s%20bosses%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98chhup%20raho%20%3C%2Fem%3E(be%20quiet)%2C%20or%20else%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20not%20a%20debate%20about%20whether%20Kishan%20should%20have%20played%20or%20not%2C%20or%20whether%20he%20should%20get%20a%20BCCI%20contract%20or%20not.%20The%20issue%20is%20the%20utter%20lack%20of%20transparency.%20The%20BCCI%20must%20be%20transparent%20about%20how%20they%20arrived%20at%20this%20decision%2C%20what%20conversations%20were%20had%20with%20Kishan%20through%202023%2C%20and%20how%2C%20despite%20all%20checks%20and%20balances%2C%20he%20went%20off%20track%2C%20if%20indeed%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05144605%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-05-at-2.45.37-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22649%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05144605%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-05-at-2.45.37-PM.png%20498w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05144605%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-05-at-2.45.37-PM-300x153.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700201%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22331%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%20(left)%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIshan%20episode%20will%20impact%20our%20young%20guns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20is%2C%20Team%20India%20has%20many%20youngsters.%20Superbly%20talented.%20With%20tough%20back%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20done%20well%20on%20the%20back%20of%20this%20bank%20of%20young%20talent.%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20is%2022.%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20and%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20are%2023.%20Shubman%20Gill%20is%2024.%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20and%20Rinku%20Singh%20are%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20need%20career%20management%2C%20they%20need%20counselling%20off%20the%20field%2C%20their%20mental%20health%20should%20be%20a%20huge%20concern%20at%20all%20times.%20But%20is%20this%20happening%3F%20If%20Kishan%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20an%20indicator%2C%20not%20enough.%20This%20episode%20may%20have%20brought%20uncertainty%20and%20fear%20back%20into%20the%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fdear-bcci-deepti-sharma-and-indias-women-in-blue-deserve-better%5C%22%3EDear%20BCCI%2C%20Deepti%20Sharma%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Women%20in%20Blue%20Deserve%20Better%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20also%20compounding%20the%20problem%20with%20knee-jerk%20reactions.%20The%20sudden%20tough%20talk%20on%20playing%20Ranji%20trophy%20comes%20after%20years%20of%20signalling%20to%20players%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20matter.%20A%20lot%20of%20team%20selection%20decisions%20seem%20to%20have%20relied%20on%20the%20IPL%20form%20of%20players%20in%20recent%20years.%20If%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20a%20must%20for%20every%20player%20in%20Team%20India%2C%20it%20must%20be%20enforced%20for%20all%2C%20without%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20lets%20talk%20about%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20who%20has%20also%20lost%20his%20BCCI%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20equally%20curious%20case%20of%20Shreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIyer%20played%20the%20first%20two%20Test%20matches%20of%20the%20on-going%20series%20against%20England%2C%20till%20February%205.%20He%20was%20then%20dropped%2C%20even%20though%20he%20actually%20scored%20more%20runs%20than%20Sharma%20in%20the%20two%20Tests.%20As%20he%20left%2C%20he%20also%20complained%20of%20back%20spasms%2C%20a%20problem%20that%20forced%20him%20to%20miss%20IPL%202023.%20He%20had%20just%20three%20weeks%20before%20the%20BCCI%20contracts%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20three%20weeks%20could%20he%20have%20been%20given%20the%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20about%20his%20back%20pain%3F%20Apparently%20not%2C%20since%20he%20had%20to%20be%20made%20an%20example%20of.%20The%20%C2%A0National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20have%20seemed%20to%20%E2%80%98help%E2%80%99%20by%20rubbishing%20Iyer%E2%80%99s%20back%20pain%20claim%2C%20despite%20reports%20that%20the%20Mumbai%20Ranji%20coach%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20back%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2028%2C%20Iyer%20lost%20his%20BCCI%20contract%2C%20for%20failing%20to%20play%20a%20Ranji%20match%20over%20a%20period%20of%20three%20weeks.%20What%20then%2C%20about%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20who%20according%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhen-was-last-time-kl-rahul-turned-up-for-ranji-game-fresh-kkr-camp-details-emerge-shreyas-iyer-bcci-contract-saga-101709357768803.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20not%20played%20a%20Ranji%20match%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20Sure%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20proven%20talent%20and%20deserves%20his%20Rs%205%20core%20A%20grade%20contract.%20But%20does%20Iyer%20suddenly%20deserve%20nothing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20a%20system%20of%20%E2%80%98different%20rules%E2%80%99%20for%20%E2%80%98different%20folks%E2%80%99.%20Even%20if%20Iyer%20%E2%80%98deserved%E2%80%99%20a%20rap%20on%20the%20knuckles%2C%20could%20he%20have%20just%20been%20%E2%80%98down-graded%E2%80%99%3F%20Why%20is%20he%20suddenly%20not%20even%20in%20the%20pool%20of%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%2030%20contracted%20players%3F%20Is%20he%20being%20punished%20for%20%E2%80%98crimes%E2%80%99%20that%20we%20are%20not%20aware%20of%3F%20And%20again%2C%20Iyer%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20silent%2C%20so%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20his%20version.%20This%20again%2C%20is%20lack%20of%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20Hardik%20Pandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20Hardik%20Pandya%20get%20away%20with%20it%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%2C%20everyone%20except%20BCCI%20knows%20that%20Pandya%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20playing%20Test%20cricket.%20But%20when%20touring%20the%20SENA%20(South%20Africa%2C%20Australia%2C%20England%2C%20New%20Zealand)%20countries%2C%20as%20a%20fast-bowling%20and%20batting%20all-rounder%2C%20he%20would%20be%20an%20asset.%20So%2C%20if%20he%20is%20not%20keen%20to%20put%20country%20before%20self%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20BCCI%20have%20a%20rethink%20about%20his%20contract%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Pandya%20has%20nursed%20an%20injury%20right%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20red-ball%20cricket%20season%20this%20winter%2C%20playing%20neither%20Test%20matches%20nor%20Ranji%20trophy%20matches.%20Equally%20interesting%2C%20he%20has%20not%20said%20on%20record%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20give%20up%20red-ball%20cricket%2C%20which%20gives%20BCCI%20enough%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98fig%20leaf%E2%80%99%20to%20award%20him%20a%20full%20grade%20A%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara.%20Yes%2C%20he%20is%20in%20the%20autumn%20of%20his%20career.%20But%2C%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20young%20guns%20yet%20to%20stabilise%2C%20could%20Pujara%20have%20been%20retained%20in%20the%20pool%20of%2030%20and%20been%20given%20a%20contract%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEspecially%20since%20he%20has%20been%20doing%20exactly%20what%20BCCI%20has%20prescribed%20%E2%80%93%20play%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20score%20big%20and%20stay%20in%20contention%20%E2%80%93%20he%E2%80%99s%20done%20both%20this%20season%2C%20only%20to%20be%20overlooked.%20Talk%20about%20%E2%80%98confused%E2%80%99%20messaging%2C%20and%20double%20standards%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPujara%2C%20Chahal%20and%20double%20standards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20story%20of%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20%E2%80%93%20our%20foremost%20spinner%20in%20T20%20cricket%20till%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dip%20in%20the%20form%20cost%20him%20his%20place%20in%20the%20team.%20Fine.%20But%2C%20suddenly%20he%20finds%20himself%20without%20a%20contract.%20Surely%2C%20he%20is%20still%20good%20enough%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20pool%20of%2030%20contracted%20players.%20And%20again%2C%20no%20clear%20reason%20shared%20with%20the%20media%20or%20the%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20he%20was%20counselled%2C%20or%20whether%20as%20a%20senior%20player%2C%20did%20Agarkar%20and%20Dravid%20speak%20with%20him%20and%20explain%20their%20decision%20to%20him.%20And%20Chahal%20too%2C%20is%20obliged%20to%20stay%20silent%2C%20for%20fear%20of%20upsetting%20the%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20high%20priests.%20Is%20this%20fair%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20we%E2%80%99re%20talking%20about%20spinners%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BCCI%20has%20now%20come%20up%20with%20a%20good%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98fast%20bowling%20contracts%E2%80%99%20for%20pacers%20on%20the%20fringe%20of%20the%20team.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20have%20%E2%80%98spin%20bowling%20contracts%E2%80%99%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20always%20had%20a%20wealth%20o