20film%2C%20without%20ever%20intruding%20and%20stating%20its%20presence.%20The%20song%20showcases%20its%20composer%20at%20his%20strongest%3B%20Sampath%20knows%20how%20to%20keep%20things%20simple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FtF1JN2pT_sM%3Fsi%3DsOT1EJe5a-t9rDLP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20man%20going%20to%20a%20police%20station%20to%20file%20a%20report%20after%20%E2%80%98misplacing%E2%80%99%20his%20wife%20%E2%80%93%20sounds%20like%20the%20first%20line%20of%20a%20WhatsApp%20joke.%20In%20her%20sophomore%20effort%2C%20Rao%20builds%20a%20gentle%2C%20hopeful%20film%20around%20this%20%E2%80%98quirky%E2%80%99%20premise.%20It%20was%20probably%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20first%20name%20I%20saw%20while%20exiting%20the%20theatre%20after%20watching%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20film%20was%20Hrishikesh%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s.%20A%20quote%20attributed%20to%20him%20reads%20something%20like%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20let%20the%20sugar%20in%20my%20films%20overpower%20the%20medicine.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20quote%20that%20sits%20well%20with%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20given%20how%20its%20feminist%20stance%20is%20conveyed%20without%20beating%20its%20audiences%20over%20their%20heads.%20Also%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20Mukherjee%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBawarchi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1972)%20quite%20a%20bit%20while%20watching%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20film.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20a%20million%20others%2C%20Deepak%20and%20Phool%20have%20just%20gotten%20married%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Nirmal%20Pradesh.%20She%E2%80%99s%20taught%20to%20walk%20with%20a%20veil%20over%20her%20head.%20When%20she%20trips%20on%20her%20way%20to%20the%20local%20bus%20stand%2C%20an%20elder%20tells%20her%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CLearn%20to%20walk%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghoonghat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20keep%20your%20eyes%20to%20the%20ground.%E2%80%9D%20When%20they%20enter%20their%20designated%20bogey%20%E2%80%93%20two%20more%20newly-married%20couples%20are%20already%20seated%20there.%20Almost%20wearing%20identical%20clothes%2C%20a%20newly-minted%20mother-in-law%20brags%20how%20the%20suit%20material%20for%20their%20son%20is%20better%20than%20Deepak%E2%80%99s.%20They%20casually%20ask%20him%20what%20he%20got%20for%20dowry%2C%20before%20going%20to%20brag%20about%20how%20their%20son%20got%20a%20motorbike%20and%20a%20cellphone%20from%20his%20in-laws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140712%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.04.17%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x496.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140712%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.04.17%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x496.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140712%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.04.17%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x145.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140712%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.04.17%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700187%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Laapataa%20Ladies%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReaching%20his%20station%20late%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Deepak%20wakes%20up%20in%20a%20daze%20and%20tells%20Phool%20to%20hurry%20and%20get%20off%20the%20train.%20But%20then%2C%20all%20hell%20breaks%20loose%2C%20when%20Deepak%20and%20his%20family%20realise%20he%E2%80%99s%20brought%20home%20another%20one%20of%20the%20(almost%20identically%20dressed)%20brides%20in%20the%20bogey.%20Pushpa%20(Pratibha%20Ranta)%20is%20nowhere%20as%20shy%20as%20Phool.%20When%20asked%20about%20why%20she%20followed%20Deepak%20without%20any%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20simply%20told%20to%20follow%20my%20husband%E2%80%99s%20shoes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20snaps%20back.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Phool%20wakes%20up%20in%20a%20station%20a%20few%20hours%20down%20the%20line%20and%20much%20to%20her%20horror%2C%20without%20Deepak%20around.%20She%20can%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20remember%20the%20name%20of%20Deepak%E2%80%99s%20village%2C%20or%20even%20the%20name%20of%20the%20station%20she%20boarded%20from.%20She%20decided%20to%20stick%20around%20there.%20Deepak%20approaches%20a%20corrupt%20cop%20Shyam%20Manohar%20for%20help%20about%20his%20missing%20wife%20%E2%80%93%20a%20glorious%C2%A0%20and%20perpetually%20pan-chewing%20Ravi%20Kishen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWritten%20by%20Sneha%20Desai%2C%20based%20on%20a%20novella%20by%20Biplab%20Goswami%2C%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20optimistic%20without%20being%20naive%2C%20assertive%20without%20being%20loud%2C%20and%20crowd-pleasing%20without%20sacrificing%20integrity%20for%20a%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98happy%20ending%E2%80%99.%20The%20two%20brides%20are%20built%20differently.%20Pushpa%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20Jaya%2C%20invites%20the%20suspicions%20of%20Shyam%20Manohar%2C%20who%20follows%20her%20around.%20Phool%2C%20out%20of%20her%20depth%20at%20a%20railway%20station%2C%20befriends%20a%20couple%20of%20people%20working%20at%20a%20food%20stall.%20But%20just%20like%20characters%20from%20an%20Imtiaz%20Ali%20film%20%E2%80%93%20just%20when%20the%20two%20brides%20lose%20themselves%20in%20this%20big%2C%20bad%20world%2C%20is%20when%20they%20end%20up%20finding%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaya%20appears%20to%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20saving%20crops%20from%20insects%2C%20also%20fearlessly%20asking%20her%20mother-in-law%20(Geeta%20Agrawal%2C%20playing%20a%20nameless%20%E2%80%98mother%E2%80%99%20character%20for%20a%20fourth%20time%20in%20the%20last%20five%20months)%20if%20she%20can%20befriend%20her.%20Even%20as%20she%20appears%20to%20be%20plotting%20something%2C%20Jaya%20goes%20around%20the%20house%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20a%20quiet%20revolution.%20Phool%2C%20who%20prides%20herself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbhale%20ghar%20ki%20ladki%E2%80%9D%20(from%20a%20%E2%80%98decent%E2%80%99%20family)%20meets%20Manju%20Maai%20(Chhaya%20Kadam)%20who%20first%20rebukes%20her%20for%20her%20%E2%80%98decency%E2%80%99%20%5BPhool%20won%E2%80%99t%20utter%20Deepak%E2%80%99s%20name%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20something%20a%20dutiful%20bride%20does%5D%2C%20and%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20employ%20her.%20Phool%20earns%20her%20first%20living%20when%20Manju%20Maai%20shoves%20some%20cash%20in%20her%20palm%2C%20telling%20her%20how%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalaakand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(sweet)%20she%20made%20is%20a%20big%20hit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.05.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x692.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.05.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x692.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.05.46%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x203.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05140634%2FScreenshot-2024-03-05-at-2.05.46%25E2%2580%25AF