%20the%20information%20available%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%20the%20interview%20he%20said%20the%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20position%20was%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20ridiculous%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gupta%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20explanation%20is%20not%20really%20worth%20much%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FL-qdDu1N3i8%3Fsi%3D9Dep7gFuQVuCYta0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20order%20of%20April%202019%2C%20when%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20bench%2C%20Justice%20Gupta%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20Court%20had%20directed%20that%20you%20keep%20this%20information%20it%20was%20their%20bounden%20duty%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20when%20a%20Court%20asks%20them%20to%20disclose%20it%20they%20should%20disclose%20it%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20Not%20that%20they%20take%20months%20to%20disclose%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%C2%A0%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20Justice%20Deepak%20Gupta%20has%20also%20said%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20it%20should%20take%20a%20few%20hours%20or%20a%20few%20days%20at%20the%20most%20to%20collate%20all%20the%20details%E2%80%9D%20and%20make%20the%20relevant%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Justice%20Gupta%20said%20that%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20admission%20it%20only%20has%2044%2C434%20sets%20of%20information.%20In%20contrast%2C%20he%20added%2C%20they%20probably%20handle%2044%20million%20each%20day%20across%20all%20their%20branches.%20Why%20then%2C%20he%20inferred%2C%20do%20they%20have%20this%20problem%20