row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20monumental%20development%20set%20to%20transform%20urban%20transportation%2C%20PM%20Modi%20is%20slated%20to%20inaugurate%20several%20key%20metro%20and%20rapid%20transit%20projects%20across%20countries%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20stride%20towards%20enhancing%20urban%20mobility%20and%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20Metro%20extension%2C%20featuring%20the%20Howrah%20Maidan-Esplanade%20Metro%20section%2C%20includes%20the%20first%20transportation%20tunnel%20in%20India%20to%20pass%20under%20a%20major%20river%2C%20representing%20a%20critical%20milestone%20in%20the%20country's%20infrastructure%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20section%20not%20only%20showcases%20the%20technological%20prowess%20involved%20in%20its%20construction%20but%20also%20highlights%20the%20strategic%20importance%20of%20connecting%20two%20bustling%20areas%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20enhancing%20the%20city's%20public%20transportation%20network's%20efficiency%20and%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20underwater%20metro%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20also%20inaugurate%20the%20Kavi%20Subhash%20-%20Hemanta%20Mukhopadhyay%20Metro%20section%20and%20the%20Taratala%20-%20Majerhat%20Metro%20section%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Joka-Esplanade%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20features%20the%20Majerhat%20Metro%20Station%2C%20an%20architectural%20marvel%20being%20an%20elevated%20station%20spanning%20railway%20lines%2C%20platforms%2C%20and%20a%20canal%2C%20further%20showcasing%20the%20innovative%20approach%20towards%20improving%20urban%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20event%20will%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20Kolkata.%20The%20PM%20Modi%20is%20set%20to%20flag%20off%20several%20other%20important%20projects%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20the%20Pune%20Metro's%20stretch%20from%20Ruby%20Hall%20Clinic%20to%20Ramwadi%2C%20the%20Kochi%20Metro%20Rail%20Phase%20I%20Extension%20from%20SN%20Junction%20Metro%20station%20to%20Tripunithura%20Metro%20station%2C%20the%20Agra%20Metro's%20stretch%20from%20Taj%20East%20Gate%20to%20Mankameshwar%20and%20the%20Duhai-Modinagar%20(North)%20section%20of%20the%20Delhi-Meerut%20RRTS%20Corridor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20these%20projects%20is%20designed%20to%20significantly%20ease%20road%20traffic%20congestion%20and%20provide%20seamless%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20comfortable%20connectivity%20for%20the%20public.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20newly%20inaugurated%20section%20of%20the%20Agra%20Metro%20is%20poised%20to%20enhance%20access%20to%20the%20city's%20historical%20and%20tourist%20sites%2C%20while%20the%20RRTS%20corridor%20aims%20to%20stimulate%20economic%20activity%20within%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20will%20also%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20Pune%20Metro%20Rail%20project%20phase%201%20between%20Pimpri%20Chinchwad%20Metro-Nigdi%2C%20promising%20continued%20expansion%20and%20enhancement%20of%20urban%20transit%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comprehensive%20initiative%20underscores%20the%20government's%20dedication%20to%20developing%20sustainable%20and%20efficient%20transportation%20networks%20across%20India%2C%20aiming%20to%20revolutionize%20the%20way%20people%20commute%2C%20reduce%20environmental%20impact%2C%20and%20bolster%20economic%20growth%20through%20improved%20connectivity.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709626800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Figbad2a8_underwater-metro_625x300_08_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-inaugurate-indias-1st-underwater-metro-in-kolkata-tom