abelling%20and%20consent%20based%20disclosure%20to%20user%20about%20untested%20platforms%20is%20insurance%20policy%20to%20platforms%20who%20can%20otherwise%20be%20sued%20by%20consumers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSafety%20and%20Trust%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Internet%20is%20a%20shared%20and%20common%20goal%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20government%2C%20users%20and%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERecent%20advisory%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGoI_MeitY%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40GoI_MeitY%3C%2Fa%3E%20needs%20to%20be%20understood%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%9E%A1%EF%B8%8FAdvisory%20is%20aimed%20at%20the%20Significant%20platforms%20and%20permission%20seeking%20from%20Meity%20is%20only%20for%20large%20plarforms%20and%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%9E%A1%EF%B8%8FAdvisory%20is%20aimed%20at%20untested%20AI%20platforms%20from%20deploying%20on%20Indian%20Internet%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3(Modiyude%20Kutumbam)%20(%40Rajeev_GoI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeev_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1764534565715300592%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20questions%20remain%20about%20which%20rule%20or%20law%20this%20advisory%20has%20suddenly%20been%20issued%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20for%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20too%2C%20rushed%20to%20list%20out%20exceptions%20for%20the%20advisory%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%20He%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20apply%20to%20any%20platforms%20working%20in%20the%20healthcare%20or%20agriculture%20sector.%20It%20will%20apply%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fai-models-must-take-permission-before-launching-to-indian-public-says-government-12388631.html%5C%22%3Ereported%20moneycontrol.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20clarified%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20missive%20was%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cregulatory%20framework%E2%80%9D%20but%20an%20advisory%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctest%20your%20model%20before%20launching%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fai-models-must-take-permission-before-launching-to-indian-public-says-government-12388631.html%5C%22%3Eadvisory%20issued%20to%20intermediaries%20on%20March%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IT%20ministry%20had%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexplicit%20permission%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20government%20was%20necessary%20to%20deploy%20AI%20models%20in%20testing%20stage.%20The%20advisory%20also%20ordered%20platforms%20%E2%80%9Cto%20label%20synthetic%20content%20with%20unique%20identifiers%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20identify%20the%20creator%20of%20misinformation%20or%20deepfake.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-advisory-rajeev-chandrasekhar%5C%22%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Modi%20a%20Fascist%3F%E2%80%9D%20answered%20with%20certainty%20by%20Google%20Gemini%20first%20caused%20a%20storm%20and%20suggested%20a%20complete%20change%20of%20mood%20about%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%20start-up%20hiccups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20start-ups%20have%20been%20complaining%20publicly%20over%20Goggle%20knocking%20them%20off%20the%20Playstore%2C%20for%20not%20paying%20a%20mandated%20share%20(11-30%25)%20for%20in-app%20payments%20received%20by%20them.%20Start-ups%20maintain%20that%20their%20revenue%20stream%20has%20collapsed%20after%20not%20being%20available%20for%20download%20on%20the%20Google%20platform.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-vs-indian-startups-apps-take-next-big-step-against-alphabet-inc-urge-cci-to-take-action-101709597173811.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Hindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20have%20approached%20the%20regulator%2C%20the%20Centre-run%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20again%2C%20to%20get%20all%20apps%20back%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20held%20talks%20with%20Google%20regarding%20the%20start-ups%20being%20removed.%20Vaishnaw%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-has-started-restoring-de-listed-indian-apps-says-it-minister-101709382530229.html%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20told%20%5BGoogle%5D%20that%20it%20must%20support%20India%E2%80%99s%20start-up%20ecosystem.%20They%20have%20already%20started%20re-listing%20the%20apps%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnaw%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CGoogle%20has%20agreed%20to%20cooperate.%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20Google%20last%20night%20%5BFriday%5D%20when%20I%20first%20learnt%20of%20this.%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20them%204-5%20times%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20first%20delisted%20apps%20by%2010%20Indian%20developers%20for%20not%20complying%20with%20its%20payments%20policy%2C%20about%20sharing%2011-30%25%20service%20fee%20with%20them%20for%20all%20in-app%20purchases%20of%20digital%20goods%20and%20services.%20Companies%20affected%20included%20Info%20Edge%E2%80%99s%20five%20apps%20%E2%80%93%20Naukri.com%2C%20Naukri%20Recruiter%2C%20Naukrigulf%2C%2099acres%20and%20Shiksha.%20By%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20three%20of%20these%20apps%20%E2%80%93%20Naukri.com%2C%20Naukrigulf%20and%2099acres%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20relisted.%20Shaadi.com%20is%20the%20only%20other%20app%20to%20be%20relisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca