e-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2Fng-interactive%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F29%2Fjay-shetty-self-help-empire%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2Fng-interactive%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F29%2Fjay-shetty-self-help-empire%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0report%20claims%20that%20the%2036-year-old%20falsely%20claimed%20to%20have%20spent%20three%20years%20in%20a%20temple%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduating%2C%20Shetty%20forgoes%20a%20life%20of%20material%20success%20to%20live%20as%20a%20monk%20himself%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0said%20the%20report.%20%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20later%2C%20he%20has%20another%20revelation%3A%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20is%20not%20to%20live%20the%20humble%20life%20of%20a%20monk%20but%20to%20use%20his%20preternatural%20oratory%20skills%20to%20share%20wisdom%20with%20the%20world.%20Thus%20begins%20his%20transformation%20into%20a%20public%20self-help%20personality%20and%20his%20swift%20rise%20to%20fame.%20Shetty's%20success%20is%20largely%20predicated%20on%20this%20riches-to-rags-to-riches%20backstory%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20the%20veracity%20of%20Jay%20Shetty's%20story%2C%20the%20report%20added%2C%20%26quot%3B%C2%A0But%20people%20close%20to%20Shetty%20have%20questioned%20whether%20his%20conversion%20to%20a%20life%20of%20monkhood%20was%20quite%20so%20dramatic.%20Much%20of%20Shetty's%20spiritual%20education%20took%20place%20not%20in%20India%20but%20in%20Watford%2C%20an%20orbital%20town%20outside%20north-west%20London%2C%20they%20say.%20He%20was%20there%20not%20because%20of%20spiritual%20discovery%20in%20college%20but%20because%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20International%20Society%20for%20Krishna%20Consciousness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20daily%20newspaper%C2%A0also%C2%A0questioned%20Mr%20Shetty's%20academic%20qualifications%2C%20pointing%20out%20discrepancies%20in%20his%20resume%2C%20including%20a%20degree%20from%20a%20business