20her%20life%20and%20told%20her%20fiance%20to%20%26quot%3Bgo%20enjoy%20the%20life%20he%20deserves.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20reading%20this%20then%20it%20means%20I%20have%20died%20from%20my%20battle%20with%20cancer%20and%20my%20family%20are%20posting%20my%20final%20message%20on%20my%20behalf.%20Firstly%2C%20I%20just%20want%20to%20say%20that%20not%20all%20cancers%20are%20caused%20by%20lifestyle%20choices%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20it's%20genetics%20or%20unfortunately%20it%20just%20happens.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20despite%20me%20being%20very%20healthy%20and%20active%2C%20a%20cancer%20started%20in%20my%20bile%20ducts%20which%20was%20not%20caused%20by%20anything%20in%20my%20control%20and%20my%20life%20was%20never%20the%20same%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Thackray%20said%20that%20she%20chose%20to%20enjoy%20every%20moment%20rather%20than%20being%20sad%20about%20it.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20we%20can't%20control%20what%20happens%20to%20us%2C%20we%20can%20control%20how%20we%20react.%20I%20chose%20not%20to%20mourn%20the%20life%20I%20was%20losing%20despite%20being%20so%20devastated%2C%20but%20to%20instead%20enjoy%20every%20moment%20I%20had%20left.%20As%20I%20have%20always%20said%20and%20believed%20you%20should%20enjoy%20the%20little%20things%20in%20life%20and%20cherish%20every%20moment!%20Romanticise%20your%20life!%20Do%20whatever%20makes%20you%20happy%20and%20don't%20let%20anyone%20take%20the%20joy%20of%20life%20away%20from%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2025-year-old%20said%20she%20loved%20everything%20that%20she%20had-%20her%20family%2C%20job%2C%20fiance%2C%20friends%20and%20dog.%20She%20also%20thanked%20everyone%20for%20making%20her%20life%20%26quot%3Bmagical.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20included%20a%20quote%20by%20A.A.%20Milne%20in%20'Winnie%20the%20Pooh'%20and%20wrote%20%26quot%3BIf%20ever%20there%20is%20a%20tomorrow%20when%20we're%20not%20together%2C%20there%20is