%20is%20so%20touching%2C%20inspiring%2C%20and%20sad%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20I%20feel%20for%20her.%3Cbr%3E%5CnPlease%20take%20this%20in%20and%20learn%20from%20this%20young%20woman%20of%20how%20to%20live%20and%20prepare%20at%20the%20same%20time.%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709622360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Flfa0mnv8_daniella-thackray_625x300_05_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-battling-cancer-writes-final-message-in-linkedin-post-tells-fiance-to-go-enjoy-life-5179509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20chose%20not%20to%20mourn%20the%20life%20I%20was%20losing%20despite%20being%20so%20devastated%2C%20but%20to%20instead%20enjoy%20every%20moment%20I%20had%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2025-year-old%20wrote%20in%20the%20message.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-battling-cancer-writes-final-message-in-linkedin-post-tells-fiance-to-go-enjoy-life-5179509%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-battling-cancer-writes-final-message-in-linkedin-post-tells-fiance-to-go-enjoy-life-5179509%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-battling-cancer-writes-final-message-in-linkedin-post-tells-fiance-to-go-enjoy-life-5179509%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20sea%20drones%20damage%20Russian%20Black%20Sea%20fleet%20patrol%20ship%20near%20Crimea%2C%20Ukraine%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709622285000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108228860%2Cimgsize-1566285.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukrainian-sea-drones-damage-russian-black-sea-fleet-patrol-ship-near-crimea-ukraine-says%2Farticleshow%2F108228817.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%