stitute%20of%20Technology%20Madras%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Father-energy-picks-hsbc-jpmorgan-nomura-indian-banks-to-arrange-its-ipo-124030500302_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20and%20the%20Curious%20Case%20of%20SBI%20Keeping%20Crucial%20Data%20in%20Physical%20Form%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105750%2F1166496076_ac2efae08c_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20afternoon%20of%20March%204%2C%202024%2C%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20filed%20an%20application%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20requesting%20the%20court%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGrant%20time%20to%20the%20Applicant%20Bank%20until%2030.06.2024%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20directions%20in%20its%20Judgement%20dated%2015.02.2024%20in%20W.P.%20(C)%20No.%20880%20of%202017%20and%20batch.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20judgment%20in%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20SBI%20to%20%E2%80%9Csubmit%20the%20details%20of%20political%20parties%20which%20have%20received%20contributions%20through%20Electoral%20Bonds%E2%80%A6to%20the%20ECI.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20SBI%20must%20disclose%20details%20of%20each%20electoral%20bond%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20and%20include%20the%20date%20of%20encashment%20and%20the%20denomination%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond.%20The%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20to%20submit%20this%20information%20to%20the%20ECI%20within%20three%20weeks%20from%20the%20date%20of%20this%20judgment%2C%20that%20is%2C%20by%20March%206%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%20makes%20some%20startling%20disclosures%2C%20possibly%20inadvertently.%20The%20main%20one%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20data%20was%20not%20stored%20digitally.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20the%20application%20speak%20for%20itself%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C10.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edonor%20details%20were%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20designated%20branches%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eall%20such%20sealed%20covers%20were%20deposited%20in%20the%20Main%20Branch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Applicant%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C11.%20On%20the%20other%20end%2C%20each%20political%20party%20was%20required%20to%20maintain%20a%20designated%20account%20in%20any%20of%20the%2029%20authorised%20Branches.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20this%20account%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20received%20by%20that%20party%20could%20be%20deposited%20and%20redeemed.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20redemption%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20original%20bond%2C%20the%20pay-in%20slip%20would%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20SBI%20Mumbai%20Main%20Branch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C13.%20It%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20retrieval%20of%20information%20from%20each%20silo%20and%20the%20procedure%20of%20matching%20the%20information%20of%20one%20silo%20to%20that%20of%20the%20other%20would%20be%20a%20time%20consuming%20exercise.%20The%20details%20are%20stored%20separately%2C%20some%20of%20the%20details%20such%20as%20number%20of%20Bonds%2C%20etc.%20are%20stored%20digitally%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20other%20set%20of%20details%20such%20as%20name%20of%20purchaser%2C%20KYC%20etc.%2C%20are%20stored%20physically%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20purpose%20of%20not%20storing%20all%20details%20digitally%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20gathered%20easily%20to%20achieve%20the%20object%20of%20the%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20italics%20were%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3Efirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20thing%20that%20astounds%20is%20the%20storage%20of%20data%20in%20%E2%80%9Cphysical%E2%80%9D%20form%2C%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20indeed%20amazing%20that%20the%20SBI%20expects%20anyone%2C%20least%20of%20all%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20been%20working%20very%20diligently%20to%20digitalise%20its%20own%20working%2C%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20largest%20bank%20of%20a%20country%2C%20which%20is%20the%20world%20leader%20in%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%2C%20is%20keeping%20such%20critical%20data%20in%20physical%20form.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Cstrong%3Esecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20what%20the%20application%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20paragraph%2012%20above%2C%20says%20about%20the%20internal%20working%20of%20the%20SBI.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20us%20imagine%20a%20scenario%20that%20(a)%20a%20purchaser%20buys%20an%20electoral%C2%A0%20bond%20worth%20Rs%2010%20crores%20at%20the%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20at%20Parliament%20Street%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20(b)%20gives%20it%20to%20an%20eligible%20political%20party%20in%20Patna%2C%20(c)%20the%20political%20party%20presents%20this%20electoral%20bond%20for%20redemption%20at%20the%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20at%20Kolkata%20where%20it%20has%20a%20designated%20account%20for%20this%20purpose%20(which%20it%20is%20legally%2C%20under%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20as%20it%20existed%2C%20permitted%20to%20do)%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20electoral%C2%A0%20bond%20by%20SBI%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20application%2C%20and%20paragraph%2012%20in%20particular%2C%20seem%20to%20indicate%20that%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a)%20SBI%20New%20Delhi%20will%20send%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdonor%20details%E2%80%9D%20such%20as%20the%20KYC%20particulars%20of%20the%20purchaser%20to%20SBI%20Main%20Branch%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20in%20a%20physical%20form%2C%20without%20keeping%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(b)%20SBI%20Kolkata%20will%20deposit%20Rs%2010%20crores%20in%20the%20designated%20account%20of%20the%20political%20party%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eapparently%20without%20any%20reference%20to%20or%20verification%20from%20the%20SBI%20New%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20send%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20original%20bond%2C%20the%20pay-in%20slip%E2%80%A6in%20a%20sealed%20cover%E2%80%A6to%20the%20SBI%20Mumbai%20Main%20Branch%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20paragraph%2011%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20interesting%20facet%20is%20the%20chronology%2C%20though%20it%20is%20very%20short.%20The%20direction%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20was%20given%20to%20the%20SBI%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015%2C%20and%20the%20application%20was%20filed%20on%20March%204.%20It%20took%20the%20largest%20bank%20in%20the%20country%2017%20days%2C%20from%20February%2016%20to%20March%2003%2C%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20it%20cannot%20provide%20the%20information%20by%20March%206%20but%20will%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20it%20only%20by%20June%2030!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEfficiency%2C%20anyone%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20other%20anomalies%20in%20the%20application.%20What%20is%20deeply%20saddening%20is%20how%20predictable%20the%20application%20is.%20The%20SC%20judgment%20was%20delivered%20on%20February%2015%2C%202024.%20Speculation%20appeared%20very%20soon%20thereafter%20that%20ways%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Felectoral-bonds-bank-rules-may-impede-revealing-poll-bond-information-say-government-sources%2Farticleshow%2F107764097.cms%5C%22%3Efound%20to%20impede%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20piece%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fcomment%2Fopportunity-to-save-democracy-from-big-money-592142%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EApprehensions%20were%20expressed%20in%20some%20quarters%20soon%20after%20the%20judgment%20about%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20disclosures%20directed%20by%20the%20court%20may%20actually%20not%20happen%20and%20ways%20may%20be%20found%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20happening.%20The%20fact%20that%20these%20apprehensions%20may%20not%20be%20completely%20baseless%20is%20shown%20in%20a%20report%20published%20in%20a%20leading%20newspaper%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20very%20issue%20was%20also%20discussed%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fpodcast%2Fwhat-the-electoral-bonds-verdict-of-the-supreme-court-implies-in-focus-podcast%2Farticle67853168.ece%5C%22%3Epodcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20matter%20now%20rests%20with%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20the%20land.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20this%20momentous%20judgment%20is%20taken%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion%20or%20will%20it%20be%20a%20victim%20of%20one%20of%20the%20best-known%20laws%20of%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EC.%20Northcote