aba%2C%20along%20with%20journalist%20Prashant%20Rahi%2C%20Mahesh%20Tikri%2C%20Hem%20Keshwdatta%20Mishra%20and%20Vijay%20Nan%20Tikri%20of%20all%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandu%20Narote%2C%20the%20sixth%20person%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20was%20convicted%20earlier%20in%202017%2C%20died%20in%20August%202022%2C%20due%20to%20alleged%20delay%20in%20treatment%20while%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20detailed%20order%20is%20awaited%20and%20the%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20when%20the%20order%20copy%20is%20available.%20The%20court%20had%20concluded%20the%20hearing%20and%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20in%20September%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20two%20years%20that%20the%20Nagpur%20bench%20has%20acquitted%20Saibaba%20and%20others.%20On%20October%2014%2C%202022%2C%20the%20same%20court%2C%20comprising%20of%20Justice%20Rohit%20B.%20Deo%20and%20Anil%20Pansare%20had%20overturned%20the%20Gadchiroli%20session%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement.%20Barring%20Tikri%2C%20who%20was%20convicted%20to%2010%20years%20rigorous%20punishment%2C%20the%20others%20were%20awarded%20life%20sentences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20discharging%20all%20five%20accused%2C%20Justice%20Deo%20had%20observed%20that%20the%20due%20process%20of%20law%20cannot%20be%20sacrificed%20at%20the%20altar%20of%20%E2%80%9Cperceived%20peril%20to%20national%20security%E2%80%9D.%20The%20bench%20directed%20the%20convicts%20to%20be%20released%20forthwith%20from%20jail%20unless%20they%20are%20accused%20in%20any%20other%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20lawyers%20appearing%20for%20Saibaba%20and%20others%20had%20challenged%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20sanction%20order%20issued%20to%20prosecute%20under%20the%20stringent%20provisions%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20They%20had%20relied%20on%20Section%2041%20(A)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20which%20clearly%20states%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20court%20shall%20take%20cognizance%20of%20any%20offence%20without%20the%20previous%20sanction%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20or%20any%20officer%20authorised%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20on%20this%20behalf%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HC%20in%202022%20had%20called%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20valid%20sanction%20order%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbad%20in%20law%20and%20invalid%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Nihalsing%20Rathod%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20on%20the%20case%20called%20today%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbold%20and%20brave%E2%80%9D%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20verdict%20only%20further%20exposes%20the%20prosecution%E2%80%9D.%20Rathod%20said%20that%20the%20verdict%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%2033-year-old%20Pandu%20Narote%2C%20%E2%80%9Can%20innocent%20man%20who%20died%20in%20jail%20awaiting%20this%20verdict%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Rahi%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Shikha%2C%20a%20young%20film%20professional%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20fighting%20for%20justice%2C%20was%20overcome%20by%20emotions.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20speechless%20right%20now.%20I%20just%20want%20to%20see%20him%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20jail%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20HC%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20central%20jail%20authorities%20had%20refused%20to%20release%20them%20immediately%20and%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20state%20government%20had%20rushed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20stay%20on%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20had%20argued%20before%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20the%20discharge%20order%20was%20passed%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20requisite%20sanction%20was%20not%20sought%20by%20the%20prosecution%20and%20not%20on%20merit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-gn-saibaba-discharges-suspend-new-abnormal%5C%22%3EStrange%20Case%20of%20G.N.%20Saibaba%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Another%20New%20Abnormal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20was%20the%20case%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202017%2C%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Gadchiroli%20district%20convicted%20Saibaba%20and%20others%2C%20including%20a%20journalist%20and%20a%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20student%2C%20for%20alleged%20Maoist%20links%20and%20for%20indulging%20in%20activities%20amounting%20to%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20Aheri%20police%20station%20in%20Gadchiroli%20district%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20had%20claimed%20that%20Saibaba%20was%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Democratic%20Front%20(RDF)%2C%20an%20alleged%20frontal%20organisation%20of%20the%20banned%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist).%20RDF%20is%20banned%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20was%20named%20as%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%20Of%20the%20electronic%20devices%20seized%20from%20his%20residence%20in%202013%2C%20the%20state%20had%20claimed%20that%20as%20many%20as%20247%20pages%20were%20found%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cincriminating%E2%80%9D.%20The%20police%20had%20further%20claimed%20that%20a%20memory%20card%20seized%20from%20Hem%20Mishra%20contained%20certain%20documents%20that%20%E2%80%9Cestablished%E2%80%9D%20Saibaba%E2%80%99s%20deep%20involvement%20in%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20banned%20terrorist%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20court%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20was%20based%20on%20the%20statements%20of%2022%20witnesses.%20Of%20them%2C%20only%20one%20was%20an%20independent%20witness%3B%20the%20rest%20were%20all%20police%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20held%20Saibaba%20and%20the%20others%20guilty%20under%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Saibaba%2C%20who%20is%2090%25%20disabled%20and%20wheelchair-bound%2C%20had%20to%20endure%20serious%20health%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%2C%20Vasantha%2C%20had%20made%20multiple%20appeals%20to%20the%20state%20and%20the%20higher%20courts%20seeking%20his%20release%20owing%20to%20his%20deteriorating%20health%20condition.%20In%20one%20of%20her%20desperate%20appeals%2C%20Vasantha%20had%20said%20that%20if%20Saibaba%20was%20not%20released%20immediately%20from%20jail%2C%20he%20might%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibility%20of%20death%20in%20Indian%20prisons%20is%20not%20unreal%2C%20given%20that%20Narote%2C%20one%20of%20his%20co-accused%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpandu-narote-gn-saibab-convict-dies-swine-flu%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpandu-narote-gn-saibab-convict-dies-swine-flu%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709706130354000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0M2_alzK4pWYd1fcyJFATs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edied%20of%20swine%20flu%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allegedly%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20medical%20care.%20Also%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Reports%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprison-custodial-death-medical-care%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprison-custodial-death-medical-care%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1709706130354000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1xCu_-gPnMZgheCqUliGnN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%202000%20people%20die%20in%20jail%20every%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0due%20to%20lack%20of%20adequate%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709617212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbombay-hc-acquits-g-n-saibaba-and-five-others-in-uapa-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saibaba%2C%20who%20is%2090%25%20disabled%20and%20wheelchair-bound%2C%20and%20the%20others%20were%20charged%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA).%20Arrested%20in%202014%2C%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20freed%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infibeam%20Avenues%20gets%20RBI's%20authorisation%20for%20payment%20aggregator%20licence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709617111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2015-08%2F19%2Ffull%2F1439991553-2753.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20said%20that%20after%20receiving%20the%20in-principle%20approval%20from%20the%20RBI%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20payment%20aggregator%20in%20October%202022%2C%20the%20company%20received%20the%20final%20authorisation%20on%20March%204%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finfibeam-avenues-gets-rbi-s-authorisation-for-payment-aggregator-licence-124030500249_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nilgiris%3A%20Water%20Shortage%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Pose%20Threats%20to%20Biodiversity%20and%20Livelihoods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105623%2Farfan-abdulazeez-SH_DiXK60XY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoonoor%20(Nilgiris)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Vasanthan%20Panchavarnam%20came%20to%20Coonoor%2030%20years%20back%20on%20a%20transfer%20from%20Chennai%20as%20a%20physician.%20The%20hilly%20district%20stole%20his%20heart%20and%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20his%20permanent%20home.%20When%20some%20friends%20who%20he%20hung%20out%20with%20became%20interested%20in%20exploratory%20walks%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20picked%20up%20the%20binoculars%20and%20started%20going%20around.%20The%20change%20we%20have%20observed%20is%20tremendous%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENilgiris%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20northwestern%20part%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fabout-district%2F%5C%22%3Ebetween%20900-2%2C636%20metres%3C%2Fa%3E%20above%20mean%20sea%20level.%20More%20than%20half%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fdepartments%2Fdepartment-of-horticulture-and-plantation-crops%2F%5C%22%3E56%25%3C%2Fa%3E)%20of%20its%20total%20area%20is%20under%20natural%20vegetation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty%20years%20back%2C%20when%20Panchavarnam%20relocated%2C%20it%20was%20a%20quiet%20town%20with%20a%20flourishing%20local%20ecology.%20The%20rolling%20grasslands%2C%20dense%20woods%20and%20cool%20climate%20captured%20the%20hearts%20of%20nature%20lovers.%20But%20once%20it%20started%20attracting%20tourists%20and%20businesses%2C%20leading%20to%20landscape%20alteration%20and%20subsequent%20warming%2C%20the%20town%20started%20to%20lose%20its%20biodiverse%20verdancy%2C%20native%20flora%2C%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETemperatures%20rise%2C%20rainfall%20becomes%20erratic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemperature%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20have%20been%20observed%20for%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%20and%20several%20references%20to%20it%20are%20found%20in%20books%20and%20hunters%E2%80%99%20journals%2C%20Panchavarnam%20tells%20us.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Neilgherries%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FNeilgherries-Robert-Baikie%2Fdp%2F1021987697%5C%22%3Etravelogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%201857%20detailing%20the%20travels%20of%20medical%20superintendent%20Robert%20Baikie%20in%20the%20district%2C%20says%20that%20between%201831%20and%201833%2C%20the%20mean%20temperature%20was%2016.8%20degree%20Centigrade%20(now%20Celsius).%20Between%201901-06%2C%20it%20was%2013.8%20degree%20Centigrade%20and%20in%202016%2C%20the%20mean%20was%2024.1%20degree%20Centigrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%222030c22a-9ba9-4406-bcf9-b627de69450e%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rising%20Annual%20Maximum%20Temperature%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%226e651210-aea3-43d0-a267-798c8323d6f1%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rising%20Annual%20Minimum%20Temperature%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20had%20begun%20exploiting%20the%20land%20over%20two%20centuries%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three%20major%20towns%20in%20the%20geographical%20domain%20from%20Kodanaadu%20to%20Naduvattam%20namely%20Coonoor%2C%20Kotagiri%20and%20Ooty%20were%20exploited%20with%20buildings%20and%20plantations%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Philip%20K.%20Mulley%2C%20a%20septuagenarian%20resident%2C%20pastor%20at%20the%20local%20church%2C%20and%20long-time%20chronicler%20of%20the%20Nilgiris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20five%20decades%2C%20the%20rainfall%20pattern%20has%20been%20changing%20in%20Nilgiris%3B%20there%20have%20been%20short%2C%20intense%20spells%20with%20drop%20in%20average%20rainfall%20in%20particular%20years%2C%20says%20S.%20Vishwanath%2C%20a%20water%20expert%20and%20educator%20based%20in%20Bengaluru.%20As%20per%20the%20department%20of%20Horticulture%20and%20Plantation%20in%20Nilgiris%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnilgiris.nic.in%2Fdepartments%2Fdepartment-of-horticulture-and-plantation-crops%5C%22%3Ethe%20average%20rainfall%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20district%20is%201%2C522.7%20mm%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%223c879821-da88-4288-8d24-a5378457efad%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Rainfall%20Pattern%20In%20The%20Nilgiris%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20aquifers%20are%20not%20recharged%20and%20so%20the%20springs%20do%20not%20flow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanath%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20springs%20do%20not%20flow%2C%20reservoirs%20do%20not%20fill%20up.%20Then%2C%20there%20is%20shortage%20of%20water%20both%20for%20nature%20and%20living%20beings.%20The%20springs%20affect%20the%20wetlands%20and%20bogs%20which%20in%20turn%20impacts%20the%20grasslands%20also.%20Moreover%2C%20with%20the%20recharge%20zones%20being%20altered%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20forest%20fires%20since%20the%20soil%20moisture%20is%20deficient.%20Temperature%20also%20increases%20because%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20humidity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201850%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmanualofnlagir00grigrich%2Fpage%2Fn5%2Fmode%2F2up%5C%22%3EBritish%20planted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tasmanian%20Blue%20Gum%20(Eucalyptus%20globulus)%20and%20Black%20Wattle%20(Acacia%20Mearnsii)%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20getting%20firewood.%20The%20weed%20species%20Lantana%20Camara%20also%20came%20into%20the%20hills%20at%20the%20time%2C%20as%20part%20of%20ornamental%20plantation.%20These%20invasive%20species%20spread%20across%20the%20pristine%20habitat%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%2C%20altering%20its%20properties%20and%20making%20it%20vulnerable%2C%20says%20Panchavarnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20spoiling%20the%20grazing%20grounds%20and%20teak%20plantations%20in%20Teppakkadu.%20Sandalwood%20also%20encountered%20a%20rare%20disease%20because%20of%20Lantana.%20Wherever%20forest%20cover%20is%20disturbed%2C%20there%20is%20Lantana%20in%20Nilgiris.%20From%20a%20diverse%20ecosystem%2C%20it%20has%20created%20an%20alternate%20one%2C%20with%20structural%2C%20nutritional%20and%20species%20simplification.%20The%20loss%20of%20diversity%20is%20further%20adding%20a%20block%20to%20mitigating%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20native%20species%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scirp.org%2Fjournal%2Fpaperinformation%3Fpaperid%3D24976%5C%22%3EShola%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20name%20used%20across%20South%20India%20to%20refer%20to%20swathes%20of%20montane%20grasslands%20and%20shrublands%20%E2%80%93%20biomes%2C%20as%20per%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%20classification.%20Shola%20habitats%20in%20the%20marshlands%20of%20Nilgiris%20comprise%20stunted%20evergreen%20trees%20and%20undulating%20meadows.%20These%20have%20moisture%20retention%20properties%20and%20act%20as%20carbon%20sinks.%20When%20it%20rains%2C%20the%20Shola%20grasslands%20absorb%20the%20water%2C%20preventing%20surface%20run-off.%20With%20its%20deep%20roots%20that%20go%20seven%20feet%20under%2C%20it%20retains%20the%20water%20underground.%20The%20Shola%20ecosystem%20supports%20the%20growth%20of%20native%20species%20that%20are%20endemic%20to%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20habitats%20are%20now%20filled%20with%20Eucalyptus%2C%20Acacia%20and%20tea%2C%20as%20also%20Lantana%2C%20none%20of%20which%20have%20soil-binding%20root%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Panchavarnam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20result%20is%20that%20the%20run-off%20is%20heavier%2C%20and%20the%20resulting%20soil%20erosion%20degrades%20the%20marshlands.%20With%20the%20dams%20taking%20over%20whatever%20is%20left%20of%20the%20marshlands%2C%20the%20drastic%20landscape%20alteration%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20temperature%20have%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20certain%20native%20bird%20species.%20Thousands%20of%20migrant%20bird%20species%20have%20stopped%20coming%20to%20the%20region.%20Woodcock%20or%20game%20bird%20that%20are%20marshlands-dependent%20are%20rare%20now.%20Egyptian%20vultures%20are%20extinct%20from%20the%20upper%20reaches%2C%20as%20is%20the%20Malabar%20civet.%20Recently%2C%20some%20lost%20species%20are%20re-colonising%20because%20of%20forest%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWoodcutters%2C%20foragers%2C%20animal-grazers%2C%20and%20hunters%20add%20to%20the%20damage.%20The%20population%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%20is%20more%20than%20700%2C000%20and%20the%20area%20is%20experiencing%20rapid%20commercialisation.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20wetlands%20are%20replaced%20by%20buildings%20within%20the%20urban%20limits%20of%20Kotagiri%20and%20Coonoor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mulley%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate-change%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClimate-change%20impact%20is%20felt%20both%20in%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%20and%20man-animal%20conflict.%20Last%20year%2C%20both%20monsoons%20failed%20and%20the%20district%20received%20heavy%20rainfall%20up%20to%2050%20cm%20overnight.%20This%20resulted%20in%20landslides%3B%20all%20the%20vegetables%20ready%20for%20harvest%20were%20washed%20away%20in%20the%20heavy%20downpour%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Azad%20Kamil%2C%20founder%2C%20Ongil%20Nature%20Trust%2C%20an%20NGO%20in%20Coonoor%20that%20works%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20nature%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.s3waas.gov.in%2Fs339461a19e9eddfb385ea76b26521ea48%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F2018040983.pdf%5C%22%3Enative%20tribes%3C%2Fa%3E%20viz.%20Kurumbars%2C%20Irulars%2C%20Todas%2C%20Paniyars%20and%20Kattunayakars%2C%20many%20locals%20have%20left%20their%20properties%20behind%20and%20migrated%20to%20the%20plains%20in%20search%20of%20reliable%20occupations.%20Meanwhile%2C%20in%20localities%20like%20Rambla%20that%20are%20dominant%20with%20tea%20estates%2C%20many%20gated%20communities%20have%20mushroomed.%20This%20area%20was%20habituated%20by%20species%20such%20as%20Sambar%20deer%2C%20rabbits%2C%20Leopard%20and%20leopard%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20afforestation%20and%20encroachment%2C%20these%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20habitat%20to%20thrive.%20In%20fact%2C%20large%20carnivores%20are%20lesser%20in%20number%20now%20and%20so%20the%20population%20of%20herbivores%20such%20as%20bison%20and%20bears%20have%20become%20more%20and%20they%20are%20entering%20the%20towns%20and%20turning%20into%20a%20menace%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Panchavarnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%20cobras%20are%20not%20found%20in%20winters.%20But%20two%20Cobras%20were%20rescued%20last%20week%20in%20Kethi.%20Two%20years%20back%2C%20we%20rescued%20a%2013-foot%20King%20Cobra%20in%20Kattery%2C%20located%203%20km%20from%20Coonoor.%20Peacocks%2C%20abundant%20originally%20in%20Mudhumalai%2C%20are%20sighted%20in%20Coonoor.%20The%20most%20important%20is%20mosquitoes%20in%20the%20hills%20during%20winter%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Kamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUndoing%20the%20damage%20and%20restoring%20balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20change%20being%20experienced%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20is%20anthropogenic.%20Lantana%2C%20that%20is%20present%20everywhere%20except%20the%20upper%20reaches%2C%20cannot%20be%20removed%20totally%2C%20says%20Panchavarnam%2C%20because%20if%20even%20a%20small%20root%20is%20left%2C%20it%20grows%20and%20spreads%20rapidly.%20Also%2C%20because%20of%20the%20inedible%20nature%20of%20its%20leaves%2C%20herbivores%20cannot%20consume%20it.%20But%20the%20berries%20are%20edible%20and%20so%20the%20seeds%20get%20dispersed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20conserve%20the%20remaining%20ecosystem%20and%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%20and%20water%20shortages%2C%20says%20Vishwanath%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20focus%20on%20spring%20protection%20and%20rejuvenation%20and%20identifying%20and%20conserving%20natural%20recharge%20zones%20is%20essential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department%20conducted%20a%20campaign%20to%20remove%20many%20exotic%20species%20in%20the%20Nilgiris%20biosphere%20reserve%2C%20such%20as%20Acacia%20mearnsii%2C%20and%20the%20native%20sholas%20planted%20in%20the%20region%20have%20started%20to%20reoccupy%20the%20canopy%20gaps%2C%20said%20Rekha%20R.%20Warrier%2C%20a%20scientist%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Forest%20Genetics%20and%20Tree%20Breeding%20(IFGTB)%2C%20Coimbatore.%20Being%20unique%2C%20the%20sholas%20require%20a%20long-term%20perspective%20and%20a%20socioecological%20landscape%20management%20process%20implemented%20in%20a%20participatory%20manner%20with%20Indigenous%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20communities%20interested%20in%20protecting%20their%20traditional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fao.org%2Fdocuments%2Fcard%2Fen%2Fc%2Fcc8955en%5C%22%3Ecase%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20conducted%20and%20reported%20as%20part%20of%20a%20working%20paper%20on%20forest%20and%20Landscape%20Restoration%20supported%20by%20the%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organization%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20three%20selected%20shola%20pockets%20in%20Nilgiris%20suggest%20that%20these%20open%20patches%20should%20be%20fenced%2C%20and%20that%20native%20species%20should%20be%20reintroduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpecies%20able%20to%20establish%20in%20open%20landscapes%2C%20such%20as%20Syzygium%20cumini%2C%20can%20be%20beneficial%20in%20restoration%20initiatives.%20Of%20course%2C%20projected%20changes%20in%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20temperature%20could%20endanger%20intolerant%20endemic%20species%2C%20due%20to%20their%20narrow%20genetic%20base%20and%20restoration%20of%20species%20with%20small%20population%20sizes%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20and%20introduction%20from%20adjacent%20forest%20patches%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20increase%20their%20genetic%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic-led%20conservation%20efforts%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20district%20collector%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20are%20aimed%20at%20replanting%20Shola%20grass%20and%20remapping%20water%20resources%20to%20prevent%20further%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administrators%20need%20to%20bring%20strict%20rules%20and%20follow%20them%20diligently%2C%20feel%20residents.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Nilgiris%20biosphere%20zone%20should%20be%20considered%20in%20isolation%20%E2%80%93%20the%20general%20conservation%20rules%20made%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20applicable%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mulley%20voices%20the%20collective%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeveloping%20a%20carrying%20capacity%20and%20environmental%20management%20plan%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20relooking%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Freport-of-the-western-ghats-ecology-expert-panel%2F%5C%22%3EGadgil%20Committee%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20and%20implementing%20its%20recommendations%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fearthcheckindia%2Fnilgiris-reel-under-water-shortage-climate-change-897217%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20IndiaSpend.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709616787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05105623%2Farfan-abdulazeez-SH_DiXK60XY-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fni