0It%20found%20that%20much%20of%20the%20land%20that%20had%20been%20deforested%20for%20ranches%20owned%20by%20the%20three%20companies%20did%20not%20have%20permits%20to%20remove%20the%20trees%2C%20suggesting%20it%20was%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20comes%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20companies%20to%20comply%20with%20a%20new%20law%20in%20the%20European%20Union%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreen-business.ec.europa.eu%2Fdeforestation-regulation-implementation_en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEU%20Deforestation%20Regulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20draws%20near%20(December%2030%2C%202024%20and%20June%2030%2C%202025%20for%20micro%20or%20small%20businesses).%20According%20to%20the%20EUDR%2C%20all%20companies%20that%20sell%20goods%20to%20the%20EU%20will%20need%20to%20prove%20that%20their%20produce%20was%20not%20grown%20on%20land%20deforested%20after%202020%2C%20or%20else%20face%20heavy%20fines.%20Observers%20say%20that%20this%20law%20will%20penalise%20smallholder%20farmers%20unable%20to%20provide%20the%20relevant%20data%20needed%20to%20comply%2C%20cutting%20off%20important%20streams%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20some%20of%20the%20products%20affected%20by%20this%20law%20will%20be%20beef%2C%20coffee%2C%20palm%20oil%20and%20soy.%20Global%20Witness%20campaigners%20take%20another%20issue%20with%20the%20law%2C%20however%2C%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20not%20stringent%20enough%2C%20as%20its%20current%20wording%20means%20that%20unlike%20the%20Amazon%2C%20the%20Cerrado%20plains%20are%20not%20fully%20covered%20by%20the%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20following%20chart%20shows%2C%20Brazil%20was%20the%20biggest%20exporter%20of%20beef%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdownloads.usda.library.cornell.edu%2Fusda-esmis%2Ffiles%2F73666448x%2Fcn69nh059%2Fzs25zp436%2Flivestock_poultry.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3