upply%20the%20material%20back%20to%20industry%20players%20who%20can%20produce%2095%25%20of%20the%20battery%20bank%20back%20from%20recycled%20materials.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbatxenergies.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBatX%20Energies%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709304552000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Founders-1709299079.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Established%20in%202020%2C%20BatX%20Energies%20extracts%20rare%20earth%20metals%2C%20such%20as%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%20and%20manganese%20from%20used%20Lithium-ion%20cells%20and%20sells%20them%20to%20electric%20vehicle%20manufacturers%20or%20repurposes%20them%20(used%20Li-ion%20cells)%20into%20batteries%20for%20off-grid%20solar%20EV%20chargers%2C%20inverters%2C%20etc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343647%2Fstartup-recycling-repurposing-millions-of-lithium-ion-batteries-batx-energies-electric-vehicles%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Truth%20Social%20Co-Founders%20Sue%20Company%2C%20Claim%20Trump%20Tried%20To%20Dilute%20Shares%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20created%20Truth%20Social%2C%20and%20now%20the%20beneficiary%20of%20that%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20lawyer%20said%20as%20the%20company%20seeks%20a%20%244%20billion%20merger%20deal.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709243782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F65e0eb9023000032006562f9.jpeg%3Fcache%3DssbWdcr7ni%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftruth