20fixed%20with%20a%20man%20who%20was%2010%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20At%20my%20%3Cem%3Ehaldi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eceremony%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20team%20from%20the%20NGO%20came%20to%20my%20rescue%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20police%2C%20my%20marriage%20was%20stopped.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20Pune%20and%20continued%20my%20higher%20studies%20till%20class%2012%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20in%20a%20bank.%20Whatever%20I%20am%20today%20is%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20this%20NGO%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20long-term%20impact%20post-handholding%2C%20Manjusha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20we%20organised%20an%20alumni%20meet%20of%20our%20200%20students.%20It%20was%20really%20overwhelming%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20these%20children%20are%20doing%20well%20in%20their%20lives.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20working%20with%20multinational%20companies%2C%20some%20of%20them%20have%20become%20principals%20of%20schools%2C%20and%20some%20are%20working%20at%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20but%20as%20civil%20engineers%20and%20not%20as%20labourers.%20The%20impact%20motivates%20us%20to%20keep%20on%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Manjusha%20Doshi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709218222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FTMCP-1709217275.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343596%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20belief%20that%20every%20child%20has%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20education%2C%20health%20care%2C%20and%20a%20secure%20future%2C%20Tara%20Mobile%20Creches%20Pune%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%20With%20its%20mobile%20cr%C3%A8ches%2C%20it%20has%20catered%20to%201%20lakh%20such%20kids.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shiv