oreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325192%2Fsaakshi-gulati-nikita-mathur-travel-with-kids-india-plan-vacations-for-moms-kids-toddlers-baby%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enear%20Mahabalipuram%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaaman%20has%20over%20380%20dogs%20in%20their%20care%2C%20of%20which%2042%20are%20paraplegic%20puppies%20and%20more%20than%2050%20are%20either%20partially%20blind%2C%20blind%20or%20have%20neurological%20issues.%20The%20shelter%20is%20also%20home%20to%20more%20than%20100%20paraplegic%20adult%20dogs%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20old%2C%20abandoned%20and%20suffer%20from%20other%20disabilities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20six%20full-time%20staff%20members%20(all%20women)%2C%20Sarah%20and%20Gerry%20spend%20their%20days%20feeding%2C%20treating%2C%20rehabilitating%2C%20and%20caring%20for%20these%20forgotten%20creatures.%20Despite%20their%20abiding%20love%20for%20these%20dogs%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20task.%20From%20offering%20lifelong%20care%20for%20these%20abandoned%20dogs%20to%20raising%20funds%20for%20them%2C%20these%20five%20years%20have%20been%20extremely%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Sarah%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20see%20a%20video%20of%20a%20dog%20suffering%20or%20people%20ask%20you%20to%20rescue%20a%20dog%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20no.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20only%20option%20for%20old%2C%20blind%20or%20paraplegic%20dogs%20is%20euthanasia.%20Nobody%20will%20let%20them%20survive%20on%20the%20street.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20live%20with%20the%20guilt%20of%20refusing%20shelter%20to%20a%20dog%20who%20needs%20it.%20I%20would%20rather%20see%20them%20alive%20than%20put%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dog%20Shelter%20and%20Home%20by%20MARS%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F6-2-1708958233-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343230%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20Iyer%20feeding%20the%20dogs%20at%20her%20shelter%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20PK%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20Sarah%20relocated%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20Chennai%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20Mumbai.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Sarah%20had%20completed%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%2C%20trained%20to%20become%20a%20tutor%20for%20children%20with%20special%20needs%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20my%20daughter%20finished%20high%20school%20and%20left%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285225%2Fwhen-an-indian-mp-challenged-racism-in-america-forced-us-govt-to-apologise%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20study%20for%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20I%20took%20a%20break%20from%20everything%2C%20including%20teaching.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20first%20got%20the%20time%20to%20get%20into%20animal%20(dog)%20welfare%20full%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah%2C%20speaking%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20were%20three%20major%20events%20which%20would%20take%20Sarah%20to%20where%20she%20is%20today.%20Around%20a%20decade%20back%20on%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%2C%20they%20were%20living%20on%20Harrington%20Road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20just%20watched%20the%20movie%20PK.%20Like%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20alien%20character%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20this%20puppy%20just%20appeared%20in%20our%20lives%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20We%20heard%20a%20dog%20crying%20but%20assumed%20that%20someone%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20had%20just%20brought%20a%20young%20pup%20who%20was%20crying.%20But%20by%208%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20I%20felt%20something%20was%20wrong.%20So%2C%20I%20stepped%20out%20of%20our%20home%20and%20finally%20found%20this%20black%20and%20white%20puppy%20wedged%20between%20a%20parked%20car%20and%20the%20wall%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20initial%20attempts%20at%20pulling%20this%20puppy%20out%20weren%E2%80%99t%20successful.%20Though%20injured%2C%20he%20was%20feisty%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20touch%20him.%20Gerry%20finally%20managed%20to%20pull%20this%20pup%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20vet%20on%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve.%20We%20eventually%20found%20one%20but%20had%20to%20pay%20five%20times%20the%20rate%20to%20get%20them%20over%20to%20our%20locality%20and%20give%20it%20first%20aid.%20On%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20all%20clinics%20were%20shut.%20We%20could%20only%20take%20PK%20for%20treatment%20on%20the%202nd%20(of%20January).%C2%A0Having%20a%20spinal%20compression%20and%20a%20broken%20leg%2C%20PK%20was%20paralyse