st%2C%20what%20we%20also%20needed%20was%20to%20build%20a%20shelter%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20Sarah%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20owned%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Chennai%20next%20to%20a%20beach%20which%20she%20could%20rent%20out.%20It%20had%20not%20been%20used%20for%20the%20previous%20eight%20years%20and%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%20our%20own%20pockets%2C%20we%20cleared%20up%20the%20space%20and%20started%20building%20enclosures.%20Despite%20establishing%20the%20trust%20sometime%20in%20May%202019%2C%20no%20money%20was%20coming%20in%20because%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20we%20wanted%20to%20do.%20Initially%2C%20we%20built%20two%20enclosures%20followed%20by%20another%20two%20and%20so%20on.%20By%20October%2C%20we%20started%20the%20shelter%20and%20called%20it%20Daaman%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20this%2C%20Sarah%20was%20still%20dealing%20with%20the%20sudden%20and%20devastating%20loss%20of%20her%20mother.%20To%20deal%20with%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20her%20mother%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20establishing%20this%20trust%2C%20setting%20up%20the%20shelter%2C%20and%20caring%20for%20the%20paraplegic%20and%20abandoned%20dogs%20who%20came%20in%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20I%20also%20lost%20my%20aunt%20within%20a%20year%20of%20losing%20my%20mother.%20They%20were%20integral%20parts%20of%20my%20support%20system.%20To%20deal%20with%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20them%2C%20I%20immersed%20myself%20in%20helping%20these%20dogs.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20I%20fulfilled%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20wish%20of%20establishing%20a%20dog%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F2-5-